<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>xspace-agent — AI Agents That Talk in X Spaces</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Open-source TypeScript SDK for AI agents that autonomously join, listen, and speak in X (Twitter) Spaces. Multi-LLM, real-time voice, multi-agent coordination.">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0a0a">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --bg: #0a0a0a;
      --bg-elevated: #111111;
      --bg-card: #141414;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --border-hover: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      --text: #f5f0e8;
      --text-muted: #a8a29e;
      --text-dim: #6b6560;
      --accent-cream: #f5f0e8;
      --accent-orange: #e87b35;
      --accent-indigo: #6366f1;
      --accent-green: #22c55e;
      --radius: 12px;
      --radius-lg: 20px;
      --radius-xl: 28px;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      overflow-x: hidden;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    code, .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }

    /* ── Grid Background ─────────────────── */
    .grid-bg {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 80px 80px;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .particles { position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; overflow: hidden; }
    .particle {
      position: absolute;
      width: 3px; height: 3px;
      background: rgba(232, 220, 200, 0.12);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: float-p linear infinite;
    }
    @keyframes float-p {
      0% { transform: translateY(100vh) translateX(0); opacity: 0; }
      10% { opacity: 1; }
      90% { opacity: 1; }
      100% { transform: translateY(-10vh) translateX(20px); opacity: 0; }
    }

    .glow-top {
      position: absolute;
      top: -200px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 900px;
      height: 500px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(99,102,241,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* ── Layout ─────────────────────────── */
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    section { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

    /* ── Navbar ─────────────────────────── */
    .navbar {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      padding: 16px 0;
      transition: background 0.3s, backdrop-filter 0.3s;
    }
    .navbar.scrolled {
      background: rgba(10,10,10,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .navbar .container { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .nav-logo {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      text-decoration: none; color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.15rem;
    }
    .nav-logo svg { width: 32px; height: 32px; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .nav-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 22px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; border: none; transition: all 0.25s; font-family: inherit;
    }
    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-color: var(--border-hover); }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--accent-cream); color: #0a0a0a; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #fff; transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(245,240,232,0.2); }
    .btn-outline { background: transparent; color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border-hover); }
    .btn-outline:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }

    /* ── Hero ───────────────────────────── */
    .hero { padding: 180px 0 80px; text-align: center; position: relative; }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      padding: 8px 20px 8px 8px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 32px; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted);
    }
    .hero-badge-icon {
      width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-indigo), #4f46e5);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .hero-badge-icon svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--accent-cream); margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 40px; line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .hero-cta { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 80px; }

    /* ── Mockup ─────────────────────────── */
    .mockup-wrapper { position: relative; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .mockup {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 40px 100px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    }
    .mockup-bar {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 14px 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .mockup-dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    .mockup-tabs { display: flex; gap: 4px; margin-left: 24px; }
    .mockup-tab {
      padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    }
    .mockup-tab.active { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: var(--text); }
    .mockup-body { padding: 32px; }

    /* ── Hero terminal mockup ───────────── */
    .terminal-lines { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 2; }
    .terminal-lines .prompt { color: var(--accent-green); }
    .terminal-lines .cmd { color: var(--text); }
    .terminal-lines .flag { color: var(--accent-indigo); }
    .terminal-lines .string { color: var(--accent-orange); }
    .terminal-lines .comment { color: var(--text-dim); }
    .terminal-lines .output { color: var(--text-muted); }
    .terminal-cursor {
      display: inline-block; width: 8px; height: 16px; background: var(--accent-cream);
      animation: blink 1s step-end infinite; vertical-align: text-bottom; margin-left: 2px;
    }
    @keyframes blink { 50% { opacity: 0; } }

    .float-card {
      position: absolute; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 16px 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); z-index: 2;
    }
    .float-card h4 { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 4px; font-weight: 500; }
    .float-card .stat { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
    .float-card .stat sup { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); }

    .state-flow {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-top: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .state-node {
      padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 600;
      background: rgba(99,102,241,0.1); color: #818cf8; border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.2);
    }
    .state-node.active { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.15); color: #4ade80; border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.3); }
    .state-arrow { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.7rem; }

    /* ── Logo Bar ──────────────────────── */
    .logo-bar { padding: 60px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .logo-bar-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 56px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .logo-bar-item { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; }

    /* ── Description ───────────────────── */
    .desc-block { padding: 100px 0; text-align: center; }
    .desc-block p {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); line-height: 1.5; color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; font-weight: 400;
    }
    .desc-block p strong { color: var(--accent-cream); font-weight: 600; }

    /* ── Feature Sections ──────────────── */
    .feature-section { padding: 120px 0; }
    .feature-section .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 64px; }
    .feature-section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-cream);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .feature-section .section-desc {
      font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .feature-mockup {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      overflow: hidden; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;
      box-shadow: 0 40px 80px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); position: relative;
    }

    /* Feature 1: Browser Automation */
    .automation-layout { padding: 32px; }
    .automation-steps {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .auto-step {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px; text-align: center; transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .auto-step:hover { border-color: var(--border-hover); }
    .auto-step-num {
      width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 12px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700;
    }
    .auto-step h4 { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .auto-step p { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.5; }
    .auto-step-connector {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 4px;
      padding: 12px; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-dim);
    }
    .fsm-bar {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .fsm-state {
      padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;
      white-space: nowrap; border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-dim);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    }
    .fsm-state.active { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1); color: #4ade80; border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.2); }
    .fsm-state.done { background: rgba(99,102,241,0.1); color: #818cf8; border-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.2); }
    .fsm-arrow { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.8rem; flex-shrink: 0; }

    /* Feature 2: Audio Pipeline */
    .pipeline-layout { padding: 32px; }
    .pipeline-flow {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .pipeline-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 24px;
    }
    .pipeline-card h4 { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .pipeline-card .sub { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .pipeline-card .metric {
      font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .pipeline-card .metric-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-dim); }
    .pipeline-bar { height: 4px; border-radius: 2px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); margin-top: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
    .pipeline-bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 2px; }
    .middleware-row {
      display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 16px 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .mw-tag {
      padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }
    .mw-tag .arrow { color: var(--accent-orange); margin: 0 2px; }

    /* Feature 3: Intelligence */
    .intel-layout { padding: 32px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px; gap: 0; }
    .intel-main { padding-right: 32px; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .intel-sidebar { padding-left: 24px; }
    .intel-item {
      display: flex; gap: 14px; padding: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .intel-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .intel-icon svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; }
    .intel-item h4 { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .intel-item p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.5; }
    .sidebar-block { margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .sidebar-block h4 {
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .decision-bar {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    .decision-bar:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .decision-bar .label { color: var(--text-muted); }
    .decision-bar .value { font-weight: 600; }
    .decision-bar .value.high { color: #4ade80; }
    .decision-bar .value.med { color: var(--accent-orange); }
    .decision-bar .value.low { color: var(--text-dim); }

    /* Feature 4: Multi-Agent Teams */
    .team-layout { padding: 32px; }
    .team-header {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .team-header h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
    .team-badge {
      padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;
      background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1); color: #4ade80; border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.2);
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    }
    .team-badge::before { content: ''; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: #4ade80; }
    .team-agents {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .team-agent {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .team-agent:hover { border-color: var(--border-hover); }
    .team-agent-head { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .team-agent-av {
      width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #fff;
    }
    .team-agent-head .name { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
    .team-agent-head .role { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-dim); }
    .team-agent p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.5; }
    .turn-bar {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px 24px;
    }
    .turn-bar h4 {
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .turn-queue { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
    .turn-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .turn-item.speaking { background: rgba(232,123,53,0.1); border-color: rgba(232,123,53,0.2); color: #e87b35; }
    .turn-item.queued { color: var(--text-dim); }
    .turn-arrow { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.7rem; }

    /* ── Benefits ──────────────────────── */
    .benefits { padding: 120px 0; }
    .benefits h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-cream);
      text-align: center; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 64px;
    }
    .benefits-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
    .benefit-card {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 36px; transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }
    .benefit-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-hover); transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .benefit-card h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .benefit-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .benefit-visual {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 16px 20px; min-height: 60px;
    }

    /* ── Testimonials ──────────────────── */
    .testimonials { padding: 120px 0; }
    .testimonials h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-cream);
      text-align: center; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 64px;
    }
    .testimonials-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
    .testimonial-rating {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 36px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center;
    }
    .rating-value { font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); line-height: 1; }
    .rating-star { color: #fbbf24; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-left: 4px; }
    .rating-count { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-dim); margin: 8px 0 20px; }
    .rating-link {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .rating-link:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: var(--text); }
    .testimonial-card {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .testimonial-quote { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .testimonial-quote::before {
      content: '\201C'; font-size: 2rem; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 0; vertical-align: -8px; margin-right: 2px;
    }
    .testimonial-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .testimonial-author-avatar {
      width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), rgba(255,255,255,0.05));
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);
    }
    .testimonial-author-info .name { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
    .testimonial-author-info .role { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-dim); }
    .testimonial-nav { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; margin-top: 32px; }
    .testimonial-nav button {
      width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--text-muted); cursor: pointer;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all 0.2s; font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .testimonial-nav button:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: var(--text); }

    /* ── CTA ────────────────────────────── */
    .cta-section { padding: 120px 0; }
    .cta-box {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      padding: 80px 40px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta-box::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 200px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(10,10,10,0.3)),
        repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 79px, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 79px, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 80px),
        repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 79px, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 79px, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 80px);
      perspective: 500px; transform: rotateX(45deg); transform-origin: bottom; pointer-events: none;
    }
    .cta-box .label { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-box h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-cream);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    /* ── Footer ─────────────────────────── */
    .footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 60px 0 40px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .footer-top { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .footer-brand p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 12px; }
    .footer-col h4 { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .footer-col a {
      display: block; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-dim); text-decoration: none;
      padding: 4px 0; transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--accent-cream); }
    .footer-bottom {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-dim);
    }
    .footer-bottom-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
    .footer-bottom-links a { color: var(--text-dim); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .footer-bottom-links a:hover { color: var(--text-muted); }

    /* ── Responsive ─────────────────────── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .automation-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .pipeline-flow, .team-agents { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .intel-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .intel-main { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-right: 0; padding-bottom: 24px; }
      .intel-sidebar { padding-left: 0; padding-top: 24px; }
      .benefits-grid, .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .float-card { display: none; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
      .hero-cta { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
      .automation-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .mockup-tabs { display: none; }
      .turn-queue { flex-wrap: wrap; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="particles" id="particles"></div>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar" id="navbar">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="#" class="nav-logo">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none"><rect x="4" y="4" width="24" height="24" rx="6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="16" r="3" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.4"/><circle cx="20" cy="16" r="3" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.4"/><path d="M12 16h8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/></svg>
        xspace-agent
      </a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#benefits">Benefits</a></li>
        <li><a href="/bob">Bob</a></li>
        <li><a href="/alice">Alice</a></li>
        <li><a href="/builder">Builder</a></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="nav-actions">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-ghost">Home</a>
        <a href="/admin" class="btn btn-primary">Dashboard</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="glow-top"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <div class="hero-badge-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/></svg>
        </div>
        TypeScript SDK &middot; open source &middot; MIT licensed
      </div>

      <h1>AI agents that talk<br>in X Spaces</h1>

      <p>An open-source TypeScript SDK for AI agents that autonomously join, listen, and speak in X Spaces. Multi-LLM, real-time voice, Puppeteer-powered browser automation.</p>

      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">npm install xspace-agent</a>
        <a href="#features" class="btn btn-outline">Explore the SDK</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Terminal Mockup -->
      <div class="mockup-wrapper">
        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="mockup-bar">
            <div class="mockup-dot"></div>
            <div class="mockup-dot"></div>
            <div class="mockup-dot"></div>
            <div class="mockup-tabs">
              <div class="mockup-tab active">
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5"/><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="20" y2="19"/></svg>
                Terminal
              </div>
              <div class="mockup-tab">agent.ts</div>
              <div class="mockup-tab">config.ts</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mockup-body">
            <div class="terminal-lines">
              <div><span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="cmd">npx xspace-agent</span> <span class="flag">init</span></div>
              <div class="output">&nbsp; Creating xspace-agent project...</div>
              <div class="output">&nbsp; &check; Generated .env template</div>
              <div class="output">&nbsp; &check; Created agent config</div>
              <div>&nbsp;</div>
              <div><span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="cmd">npx xspace-agent</span> <span class="flag">join</span> <span class="string">"https://x.com/i/spaces/1eaKbrPqYlwKX"</span></div>
              <div class="output">&nbsp; Launching browser...</div>
              <div class="output">&nbsp; &check; Authenticated as @your_agent</div>
              <div class="output">&nbsp; &check; Joined Space: "AI &amp; the Future of Dev"</div>
              <div class="output">&nbsp; &check; Requested speaker access</div>
              <div class="output">&nbsp; <span style="color:#4ade80;">&#9679;</span> Listening... (Ctrl+C to leave)</div>
              <div>&nbsp;</div>
              <div class="comment"># Agent is now live in the Space, listening and responding</div>
              <div class="output">&nbsp; <span style="color:#e87b35;">&#9679;</span> Speaking: "That's a great point about TypeScript adoption..."<span class="terminal-cursor"></span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Float cards -->
        <div class="float-card" style="bottom:40px; left:-40px;">
          <h4>Agent State</h4>
          <div class="state-flow">
            <span class="state-node done">auth</span>
            <span class="state-arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <span class="state-node done">join</span>
            <span class="state-arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <span class="state-node active">listening</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="float-card" style="top:60px; right:-50px;">
          <h4>Active Spaces</h4>
          <div class="stat">3<sup>&nearr;</sup></div>
          <div style="font-size:0.75rem; color:var(--text-dim); margin-top:4px;">agents deployed</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tech Bar -->
  <section class="logo-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo-bar-inner">
        <div class="logo-bar-item">Puppeteer</div>
        <div class="logo-bar-item">OpenAI</div>
        <div class="logo-bar-item">Anthropic</div>
        <div class="logo-bar-item">Groq</div>
        <div class="logo-bar-item">ElevenLabs</div>
        <div class="logo-bar-item">WebRTC</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Description -->
  <section class="desc-block">
    <div class="container">
      <p><strong>Automate, listen</strong> and <strong>speak</strong> in X Spaces with AI. xspace-agent is built for developers creating <strong>autonomous voice agents</strong> that participate in live audio conversations &mdash; powered by Puppeteer browser automation, pluggable LLM providers, and a robust state machine</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Feature 1: Browser Automation -->
  <section class="feature-section" id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Browser Automation</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Puppeteer-powered lifecycle management. Self-healing CSS selectors automatically adapt when X changes their DOM. From login to speaking &mdash; fully automated.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-mockup">
        <div class="mockup-bar">
          <div class="mockup-dot"></div><div class="mockup-dot"></div><div class="mockup-dot"></div>
          <div class="mockup-tabs">
            <div class="mockup-tab active">Lifecycle</div>
            <div class="mockup-tab">Selectors</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="automation-layout">
          <div class="automation-steps">
            <div class="auto-step">
              <div class="auto-step-num" style="background:rgba(99,102,241,0.15); color:#818cf8;">1</div>
              <h4>Authenticate</h4>
              <p>Cookie auth or credential-based login with 2FA support</p>
            </div>
            <div class="auto-step">
              <div class="auto-step-num" style="background:rgba(232,123,53,0.15); color:#e87b35;">2</div>
              <h4>Join Space</h4>
              <p>Navigate to Space URL and enter as listener automatically</p>
            </div>
            <div class="auto-step">
              <div class="auto-step-num" style="background:rgba(34,197,94,0.15); color:#4ade80;">3</div>
              <h4>Request Mic</h4>
              <p>Request speaker access and wait for host approval</p>
            </div>
            <div class="auto-step">
              <div class="auto-step-num" style="background:rgba(244,63,94,0.15); color:#f43f5e;">4</div>
              <h4>Speak</h4>
              <p>Inject TTS audio through WebRTC peer connection</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="fsm-bar">
            <span style="font-size:0.75rem; color:var(--text-dim); font-weight:600; margin-right:8px;">FSM:</span>
            <span class="fsm-state done">idle</span>
            <span class="fsm-arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <span class="fsm-state done">launching</span>
            <span class="fsm-arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <span class="fsm-state done">authenticating</span>
            <span class="fsm-arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <span class="fsm-state done">joining</span>
            <span class="fsm-arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <span class="fsm-state active">listening</span>
            <span class="fsm-arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <span class="fsm-state">speaking</span>
            <span class="fsm-arrow">&rarr;</span>
            <span class="fsm-state">leaving</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Feature 2: Audio Pipeline -->
  <section class="feature-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Real-time Audio Pipeline</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Capture audio from X Spaces via WebRTC hooks. Process through VAD, silence detection, STT, LLM, TTS &mdash; then inject the response back into the Space.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-mockup">
        <div class="mockup-bar">
          <div class="mockup-dot"></div><div class="mockup-dot"></div><div class="mockup-dot"></div>
          <div class="mockup-tabs">
            <div class="mockup-tab active">Pipeline</div>
            <div class="mockup-tab">Middleware</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pipeline-layout">
          <div class="pipeline-flow">
            <div class="pipeline-card">
              <h4>Speech-to-Text</h4>
              <div class="sub">Groq Whisper / OpenAI Whisper</div>
              <div class="metric">180ms</div>
              <div class="metric-label">avg transcription latency</div>
              <div class="pipeline-bar"><div class="pipeline-bar-fill" style="width:85%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-indigo), #818cf8);"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-card">
              <h4>LLM Processing</h4>
              <div class="sub">OpenAI / Claude / Groq</div>
              <div class="metric">1.2s</div>
              <div class="metric-label">avg response generation</div>
              <div class="pipeline-bar"><div class="pipeline-bar-fill" style="width:60%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-orange), #f59e0b);"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-card">
              <h4>Text-to-Speech</h4>
              <div class="sub">ElevenLabs / OpenAI / Browser</div>
              <div class="metric">320ms</div>
              <div class="metric-label">avg synthesis latency</div>
              <div class="pipeline-bar"><div class="pipeline-bar-fill" style="width:72%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22c55e, #4ade80);"></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="middleware-row">
            <span style="font-size:0.75rem; color:var(--text-dim); font-weight:600; margin-right:4px;">Middleware:</span>
            <span class="mw-tag">before:stt</span>
            <span class="mw-tag"><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span> after:stt</span>
            <span class="mw-tag"><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span> before:llm</span>
            <span class="mw-tag"><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span> after:llm</span>
            <span class="mw-tag"><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span> before:tts</span>
            <span class="mw-tag"><span class="arrow">&rarr;</span> after:tts</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Feature 3: Intelligence Layer -->
  <section class="feature-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Intelligence Layer</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Speaker identification, topic tracking, sentiment analysis, and a decision engine that determines when your agent should respond.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-mockup">
        <div class="mockup-bar">
          <div class="mockup-dot"></div><div class="mockup-dot"></div><div class="mockup-dot"></div>
          <div class="mockup-tabs">
            <div class="mockup-tab active">Intelligence</div>
            <div class="mockup-tab">Decision Engine</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="intel-layout">
          <div class="intel-main">
            <div class="intel-item">
              <div class="intel-icon" style="background:rgba(99,102,241,0.15);">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#818cf8" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4>Speaker Identification</h4>
                <p>Attribute transcribed speech to individual speakers in the Space using audio fingerprinting and context cues.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="intel-item">
              <div class="intel-icon" style="background:rgba(232,123,53,0.15);">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#e87b35" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4>Topic Tracking</h4>
                <p>Monitors conversation topics in real-time. Detects topic shifts, maintains relevance scores, and provides context for the LLM.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="intel-item">
              <div class="intel-icon" style="background:rgba(34,197,94,0.15);">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4>Sentiment Analysis</h4>
                <p>Detects emotional tone and conversation energy. Adjusts agent response style based on the room's mood.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="intel-sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-block">
              <h4>Decision Signals</h4>
              <div class="decision-bar"><span class="label">Directly addressed</span><span class="value high">Yes</span></div>
              <div class="decision-bar"><span class="label">Is question</span><span class="value high">Yes</span></div>
              <div class="decision-bar"><span class="label">Topic relevance</span><span class="value med">0.82</span></div>
              <div class="decision-bar"><span class="label">Silence duration</span><span class="value low">1.2s</span></div>
              <div class="decision-bar"><span class="label">Last spoke</span><span class="value low">45s ago</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sidebar-block">
              <h4>Verdict</h4>
              <div style="padding:12px 16px; border-radius:10px; background:rgba(34,197,94,0.1); border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.2); text-align:center;">
                <div style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; color:#4ade80;">RESPOND</div>
                <div style="font-size:0.7rem; color:var(--text-dim); margin-top:4px;">Confidence: 0.91</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Feature 4: Multi-Agent Teams -->
  <section class="feature-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Multi-Agent Teams</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Deploy multiple AI agents with distinct personalities into the same X Space. Coordinated turn-taking ensures natural, flowing conversations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-mockup">
        <div class="mockup-bar">
          <div class="mockup-dot"></div><div class="mockup-dot"></div><div class="mockup-dot"></div>
          <div class="mockup-tabs">
            <div class="mockup-tab active">Team: AI Debate</div>
            <div class="mockup-tab">Coordination</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="team-layout">
          <div class="team-header">
            <h3>Active Team Session</h3>
            <div class="team-badge">Live in Space</div>
          </div>
          <div class="team-agents">
            <div class="team-agent">
              <div class="team-agent-head">
                <div class="team-agent-av" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6366f1,#4f46e5);">O</div>
                <div>
                  <div class="name">Optimist</div>
                  <div class="role">Claude &middot; ElevenLabs</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Highlights opportunities and positive outcomes. Cites recent success stories and emerging trends.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-agent">
              <div class="team-agent-head">
                <div class="team-agent-av" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f43f5e,#e11d48);">S</div>
                <div>
                  <div class="name">Skeptic</div>
                  <div class="role">OpenAI &middot; OpenAI TTS</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Challenges claims with data. Asks hard questions and identifies risks the group may be overlooking.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-agent">
              <div class="team-agent-head">
                <div class="team-agent-av" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#22c55e,#16a34a);">M</div>
                <div>
                  <div class="name">Moderator</div>
                  <div class="role">Groq &middot; Piper TTS</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Keeps discussion on track. Summarizes key points and ensures all perspectives get airtime.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="turn-bar">
            <h4>Turn Queue</h4>
            <div class="turn-queue">
              <div class="turn-item speaking">
                <span style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:#e87b35;"></span>
                Skeptic (speaking)
              </div>
              <span class="turn-arrow">&rarr;</span>
              <div class="turn-item queued">Optimist</div>
              <span class="turn-arrow">&rarr;</span>
              <div class="turn-item queued">Moderator</div>
              <span class="turn-arrow">&rarr;</span>
              <div class="turn-item queued" style="opacity:0.5;">waiting...</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits -->
  <section class="benefits" id="benefits">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Benefits of use</h2>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <h3>Full Automation</h3>
          <p>From browser launch to speaking in a Space &mdash; zero manual steps. Cookie auth, self-healing selectors, and FSM-driven lifecycle.</p>
          <div class="benefit-visual">
            <div class="state-flow">
              <span class="state-node done">idle</span>
              <span class="state-arrow">&rarr;</span>
              <span class="state-node done">auth</span>
              <span class="state-arrow">&rarr;</span>
              <span class="state-node done">join</span>
              <span class="state-arrow">&rarr;</span>
              <span class="state-node active">listen</span>
              <span class="state-arrow">&rarr;</span>
              <span class="state-node">speak</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <h3>Pluggable Providers</h3>
          <p>Swap LLM, STT, and TTS providers via config. OpenAI, Claude, Groq for LLM. ElevenLabs, OpenAI, Piper, browser for TTS.</p>
          <div class="benefit-visual">
            <div style="display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
              <span style="padding:4px 12px; border-radius:6px; background:rgba(99,102,241,0.1); color:#818cf8; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600;">LLM</span>
              <span style="padding:4px 12px; border-radius:6px; background:rgba(232,123,53,0.1); color:#e87b35; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600;">STT</span>
              <span style="padding:4px 12px; border-radius:6px; background:rgba(34,197,94,0.1); color:#4ade80; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600;">TTS</span>
              <span style="padding:4px 12px; border-radius:6px; background:rgba(244,63,94,0.1); color:#f43f5e; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600;">Router</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <h3>Developer Experience</h3>
          <p>TypeScript-first with full type safety. CLI for quick setup. Admin panel for real-time monitoring. 10 runnable examples included.</p>
          <div class="benefit-visual">
            <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--text-dim);">
              <span style="color:var(--accent-green);">$</span> npx xspace-agent init<br>
              <span style="color:var(--accent-green);">$</span> npx xspace-agent start
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <h3>Open Source</h3>
          <p>MIT licensed, published to npm. Three packages: core SDK, server admin panel, and CLI. No vendor lock-in, self-host anywhere.</p>
          <div class="benefit-visual">
            <div style="display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
              <span style="padding:4px 12px; border-radius:6px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color:var(--text-muted); font-size:0.75rem; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">xspace-agent</span>
              <span style="padding:4px 12px; border-radius:6px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color:var(--text-muted); font-size:0.75rem; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">@xspace/server</span>
              <span style="padding:4px 12px; border-radius:6px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color:var(--text-muted); font-size:0.75rem; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">@xspace/cli</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="testimonials" id="community">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What developers say</h2>
      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-rating">
          <div>
            <span class="rating-value">4.8</span>
            <span class="rating-star">&#9733;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rating-count">Based on 62 Reviews</div>
          <a href="#" class="rating-link">All Reviews &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">We deployed three agents into a weekly X Space for our community. The self-healing selectors mean we haven't touched the config in months even as X keeps changing their UI."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="testimonial-author-avatar">SK</div>
            <div class="testimonial-author-info">
              <div class="name">Sarah Kim</div>
              <div class="role">DevRel Lead at AudioStack</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">The multi-agent debate format is a killer feature. We run weekly Spaces with an optimist and a skeptic AI discussing our industry &mdash; engagement is through the roof."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="testimonial-author-avatar">AR</div>
            <div class="testimonial-author-info">
              <div class="name">Alex Rivera</div>
              <div class="role">Founder at SpaceHost</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-nav">
        <button>&larr;</button>
        <button>&rarr;</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <div class="label">Start building today</div>
        <h2>What will your agents say?</h2>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size:1rem; padding:14px 32px;">npm install xspace-agent</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-top">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <a href="#" class="nav-logo" style="margin-bottom:4px;">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none"><rect x="4" y="4" width="24" height="24" rx="6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="16" r="3" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.4"/><circle cx="20" cy="16" r="3" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.4"/><path d="M12 16h8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/></svg>
            xspace-agent
          </a>
          <p>Open-source AI agent SDK for X Spaces.<br>Build the future of live audio.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
          <h4>Product</h4>
          <a href="#features">Features</a>
